00:19:19,810 --> 00:19:30,996
This is all about that Legacy of Kain game because there's such a commonality between movies and games in terms of the number of people you need, the expense, the technology, right?

176
00:19:31,036 --> 00:19:38,020
These are very challenging places to try and tell a story and tell a true and pure story because there's just so much going on.

