00:20:19,275 --> 00:20:26,437
The metaphor became, imagine you're in an editing room and you have all this footage, right?

186
00:20:26,477 --> 00:20:29,118
That process where in making a movie,

187
00:20:30,011 --> 00:20:35,435
The editor sits down to do the assembly cut, and they have everything that's been filmed, this vast amount of footage.

